    An implementation of the model object 'Package Section'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Owned Member
    • Owned Package Rename
    • Owned Component Type Rename
    • Owned Classifier
    • Owned Feature Group Type Rename
    • Owned Annex Library
    • Imported Unit
    • No Annexes
    • No Properties
    • Name
